Title: Going West
Description:
Leza now walks with the ancestors of this strange land. I must look now to the living.

Kor has led a group of our scouts west deeper into the jungle.

I sent a scout of my own to investigate the crane temple. Please, $p, seek out my scout, get their report, then meet up with Kor and lend what aid you can to him.

We will join you as quickly as we are able.
ObjectivesText: Find the Sunwalker Scout near the Crane Temple.
